	dprr:hasNoteText "Monetalis. In MRR 2.447, and Index, 595, refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.277-278, no. 246, 133 B.C. He may be the C. Numitorius C. f. Lem. Named in the SC de agro Pergameno in 129 (but see L. R. Taylor, VDRR 238). Cf. Sherk, RDGE no. 12, pp. 63-73, and F. De Martino, PP, fasc. 10, 1983, 171-190, in favor of a date ca. 101.\n" .
